Parliament, Wednesday, 1 March 2023 – The Portfolio Committee on Trade and Industry has postponed its schedule meeting for today until further notice. The committee was due to receive a briefing from the Department of Trade, Industry and Competition, the International Trade Administration Commission (ITAC), National Treasure and the South African Revenue Service on the implementation of ITAC’s tariff amendment or trade remedy recommendations. The committee apologises for any inconvenience.
	
